Author: NewBullMoose
Text: JFC, on pi day last week my bosses were trying to get the interns a pie and when they asked me what kind I would like I'm certain I didn't hide the fear well. Thankfully ubereats had to cancel the order for some mixup at the store, so no pie for this guy.

Author: jayrambling
Text: My parents always know too. When I go to visit them while I'm restricting my dad will ask me every 10 minutes if I want food or he'll just make me a plate and bring it to me without asking. My mom will go through the pantry before I leave and give me a bunch of food too. It's weird, as far as they know I haven't struggled with my ED for about 5 years, but I think they subconsciously know
